    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，但要注意注册流程其实还是在LMS门户内部完成的，而登录会跳转到GradeSync服务进行身份验证。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_LMS_Portal",
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Registrarse",
        "Iniciar Sesión"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先画出顶层结构：应用启动子图包含LMS门户节点，分出注册和登录两条路径。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Inicio_del_App",
        "A",
