      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "现在细化注册流程。用户需要填写完整姓名、用户名、出生日期、性别、邮箱、手机号和密码。这些信息要分发到不同的后端服务。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Nome_Completo",
        "Nome_de_Usuario",
        "Data_de_Nascimento",
        "Género",
        "Email",
        "Número_de_Telefone",
        "Senha"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "我注意到完整姓名和GradeSync关联，用户名留在LMS门户，出生日期给课堂服务，手机号和学生数据库绑定。这样分配有什么业务考虑吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_LMS_Portal",
        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "Education_StudentDB"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，GradeSync负责成绩相关的身份档案，所以存储完整姓名；课堂服务需要年龄信息来分班；学生DB作为统一的身份存储，手机号是核心标识符。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Nome_Completo",
        "Data_de_Nascimento",
        "Número_de_Telefone"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "注册子图已添加，七个字段都指向对应的服务节点。现在处理登录流程，看起来只需要邮箱和密码两个字段？",
      "elements_involved": [
